§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ What are addition and multiplication for rationals? ⦉

  ‖ What are the identity elements? ⦉
⦉

§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We call the operation of forming rationals sums ❬rational
    addition❭. ⦉

  ‖ We call the operation of forming rational products ❬rational
    multiplication❭. ⦉
⦉

